rem Metro Holografix
rem 8/21/2017

items dirty motherboards
items used ram
items obsolete processor
items t5 cabling

do Examine Metro Holografix
 [
  print This place is mess of wires and computer parts overflowing out of cardboard
  print boxs that are scattered about. It looks like nothing works. Behind a counter
  ifflag know holografixs
   [
    print The Finn smokes Yeheyuan Filters, barely looking up at you while reading 
    print a book.
   |
    print the owner smokes Yeheyuan Filters, barely looking up at you while reading
    print a book.
   ]
 ]

ifflag know holografixs
 [
  do Examine The Finn
   [
    print He's a gaijin with leathery skin, a wide mouth, and stained teeth which are 
    print too large for his jaw. He reads a book with spider-like fingers yellowed from
    print the Yeheyuan Filters he smokes.
   ]
 |
  do Examine The Owner
   [
    print He's a gaijin with leathery skin, a wide mouth, and stained teeth which are 
    print too large for his jaw. He reads a book with spider-like fingers yellowed from
    print the Yeheyuan Filters he smokes.
   ]
 ]

ifflag know holografixs
 [
  do Talk To The Finn
   [
    print The Finn looks up at you, breaking away from his book.
    go The Finn
   ]
 |
  do Talk To The Owner
   [
    print The owner looks up at you, breaking away from his book.
    go Owner 
   ]
 ]

do Exit Shop
 [
  ifflag know holografixs
   [
    print You leave The Finn behind.
   |
    print You leave the owner behind.
   ]
  go Outside Holografix
 ]



